{
  "stem": "7722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, the factory did belong to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it did belong to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took it over and the-- and-- and the beets, because the factory used to work about three months a year, and they didn't have no beets from-- from around the farms.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they used to bring them by railroad cars from-- from other farms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My job, I used to load them up in little wagons, and I used to bring them in over there into the factory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to wash them and chop them and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was what I want to tell you, there is a-- there is a saying in Jewish, [NON-ENGLISH]-- God sends the healing before he sends the plague.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this did happen to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I used to-- It was in December, so it was cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I used to work the shift in the night time, from 12 till 8 o'clock in the morning, I used to work the shift.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't get paid for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had to work for nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to go in where they made the steam to drive the factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And over there was the guy who took-- who took care.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to throw the coal and make the steam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Ukrainian, and--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- so we were known there in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Gentiles know us, and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were known, because I-- because I-- I-- they brought all the-- all the-- all the Ukrainian know us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had a feeling, I probably hid somewhere kerosene, and everybody was sitting in the dark.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no kerosene.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
